revision.text:
{{Documentation subpage}}
{{High-use}}
<!-- Categories go at the bottom of this page and interwikis go in Wikidata. -->

== Usage ==
{{Format TemplateData|JSON={"description":
"This template can be used within a sidebar to wrap links which are normally not broken by whitespace, such as in the title.<br><noexport><br><code>&#123;&#123;wraplink&#124;link&#124;title&#125;&#125;</code></noexport>",
"params": {
  "1": {
    "label": "Link",
    "required": true,
    "type": "wiki-page-name",
    "description": "The target page"
  },
  "2": {
    "label": "Display text",
    "type": "line",
    "description": "The text displayed as the link. Defaults to the page name (i.e. like normal [[WP:piping|piping]])."
  }
} }
}}

== See also ==
{{List of nowrap-like templates}}

<includeonly>{{Sandbox other||
<!-- Categories go here, and interwikis go in Wikidata -->
[[Category:Line-handling templates]]
}}</includeonly>

